tsdb.util.iterator

Class TsIteratorIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • tsdb.util.iterator.TsIterator
      • tsdb.util.iterator.MoveIterator
        • tsdb.util.iterator.TsIteratorIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<TsEntry>, ProcessingChainEntry, ProcessingChainNode, ProcessingChainSupplier

    public class TsIteratorIterator
extends MoveIterator
    Concatenates elements of several input iterators.

    Timestamps are not checked. Elements are produced in order of input iterators. So timestamps may not be ascending.
